              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44705834/" class="">十三 念声佛号，佛就会来救我吗？</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/zifang207/" class=" " title="明远">明远</a>
                (所谓伊人，在水一方)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="44705834">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44705834/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p44705834-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class="">心外无境，但求心诚</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-06-08 15:59</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p44705834-1.jpg"></div></div><p>心外无境，但求心诚</p>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







